3. Amended the title (original title: Regulations Governing the Establishment and Compensation of Temporary Medical Care Institutions for Communicable Diseases) and 15 articles by the Department of Health, the Executive Yuan, on January 21, 2008, under Shu-Shou-Chi Order No. 0970000036
